Description: You’ll learn the basics of how to operate a computer, including typing (keyboarding), internet and email. Later, you can take classes in Microsoft Word, Outlook and Excel to learn to create simple spreadsheets and documents like a resume. We also offer online job search classes and special computer classes for non-native English speakers.
Title: Computer Classes
Topics: Keyboarding, Microsoft Excel, Microsoft Outlook/PowerPoint, Microsoft Word
